      • addPhases

        void addPhases(String... phases)
        Add phases respecting add order. e.g. 
         context.addPhases("a", "b"); // phases queue: ["a", "b"]
 context.addPhasesToEnd("e", "f"); // phases queue: ["a", "b", "e", "f"]
 context.addPhases("c", "d"); // phases queue: ["a", "b", "c", "d", "e", "f"]
        Parameters:
        phases -
